          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgS5MvTPAUracylbLb9jUvVgKP1jj7ZmkPqi_AztYBBtjuh7Th=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This is for the pharmacy, not the employees\u2014 they are lovely.\n\nWorst pharmacy I\u2019ve had to ever deal with, trying to figure out why my refill is delayed for days, I call and they tell me its out of stock, and should receive it in a couple of days. Instead of using the \u201cout of stock\u201d status they put it in \u201creviewing prescription\u201d, so it\u2019s been stuck there for another week thanks to this lazy maneuver. Mind you other Walgreens pharmacies always had the courtesy to call me for any issues with my prescription immediately. 0 stars if i could, 1 is too good even.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNIcGVUVktBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x4bdc1b27b8c815b8!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICHpeTVKA%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a year ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2024-09-07T00:37:40+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Kate N",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "103809727112911873294",
          "user_review_count": 16,
          "user_photo_count": 4,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjf49FtdTyLS0Vx8KGYVQ5hOOH7tgXXCGGFFdK97UaKRijkzam=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I can\u2019t express enough how I appreciate all the pharmacists here. Their service is the best I\u2019ve experienced in the city. I\u2019ve been sticking with them for over two years for my monthly prescriptions. They help me with all the complications of my insurance and would find ways to help me save more of my out-of-pocket balance. They also often call me to offer their free same-day delivery services, which is impressive. Shout out to Scott and Ellie for being the sweetest!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURodnREMDd3RRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x4bdc1b27b8c815b8!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDhvtD07wE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 years ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2023-03-09T20:01:03+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Jennifer Hope",
          "rating": 2,
          "contributor_id": "109240589556958635369",
          "user_review_count": 47,
          "user_photo_count": 7,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvZdpUvBxmO75CuRBDbOhB4n7pKUsXGHn5l6hFajSeioOPLO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I dislike Walgreens in general, so it would be hard for any location of this pharmacy to impress me. However the store employees, though kind, also were unable to assist me with the service I needed provided, and despite having the best intentions to work with the customer, Walgreens absolute garbage policies make it impossible even for employees who want to help to do the right thing to provide actual customer service. If I could separate the rating I would give the employees 5 stars, and Walgreens ZERO. Forced to split the difference I'm reluctantly giving 2 stars to a terrible pharmacy chain. Do yourself a favor and shop somewhere else if you can afford it.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNSMlBQVFJnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x4bdc1b27b8c815b8!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICR2PPTRg%7C%7C?hl=en",
