          "description": "TBH I would give 0 star if I could. Here is the reason: I picked up medicine for my husband in September, and asked the pharmacist if he needed my husband's insurance, he said (quote on quote): \"No, I need you to pay. \" Then charged me $150. I thought ok, this medicine is not covered by my husband's insurance.\nToday, my husband picked up exactly same medicine from another Walgreen pharmacy, he was charged only $80, cuz he was asked to provide insurance information. So IT IS COVERED BY THE INSURANCE. But the guy I talked to just TOO LAZY TO INPUT IT TO THE SYSTEM. I mean, seriously?? You literally had one job! $70 is several meals! And people need to know that someone here just doesn't take their money seriously and doesn't care at all.  That's very sad.",
